Module com.bcs2024.knapsack
Package com.bcs2024.knapsack.model

Class Parcel

java.lang.Object
com.bcs2024.knapsack.model.Parcel
Direct Known Subclasses:
ParcelPlacement
public class Parcel extends Object
Represents a parcel with specific characteristics such as value, type, shape, and ID. The Parcel class is used to manage the properties and behaviors of parcels within the knapsack problem.
